  <reg:acttitle>Heritage Conservation Act</reg:acttitle>
  <reg:title>Application Regulation</reg:title>
  <reg:amsincluded>[includes amendments up to B.C. Reg. 219/2012, July 19, 2012]</reg:amsincluded>
  <reg:content>
    <bcl:section id="d2e27" toc="false">
      <bcl:marginalnote>Provisions applicable to heritage property</bcl:marginalnote>
      <bcl:num>1</bcl:num>
      <bcl:text>For the purposes of section 23 of the <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/96187_01" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Heritage Conservation Act</in:doc></bcl:link>, sections 2, 3 (1), 8 (1) to (4), 9 and 14 to 27 of the <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/96344_01" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Park Act</in:doc></bcl:link> apply to a Provincial heritage property.</bcl:text>
      <bcl:hnote>[am. B.C. Reg. 219/2012, App. 1, s. 1.]</bcl:hnote>
    </bcl:section>
    <bcl:section id="d2e48">
      <bcl:marginalnote>McAbee Fossil Beds Heritage Site</bcl:marginalnote>
      <bcl:num>2</bcl:num>
      <bcl:subsection id="d2e56">
        <bcl:num>1</bcl:num>
        <bcl:text>For the purposes of section 23 of the <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/96187_01" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Heritage Conservation Act</in:doc></bcl:link>, in addition to the provisions listed in section 1 of this regulation, sections 11, 29.1 and 30 (5) of the <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/96344_01" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Park Act</in:doc></bcl:link> apply to the McAbee Fossil Beds Heritage Site.</bcl:text>
      </bcl:subsection>
      <bcl:subsection id="d2e68">
        <bcl:num>2</bcl:num>
        <bcl:text>Despite section 1 of this regulation, section 9 of the <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/96344_01" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Park Act</in:doc></bcl:link> does not apply to the McAbee Fossil Beds Heritage Site.</bcl:text>
      </bcl:subsection>
      <bcl:hnote>[en. B.C. Reg. 219/2012, App. 1, s. 2.]</bcl:hnote>
    </bcl:section>
    <reg:provisionsnote>[Provisions relevant to the enactment of this regulation: <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/96187_01" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Heritage Conservation Act</in:doc></bcl:link>, R.S.B.C. 1996, c. 187,  section 23 (2)]</reg:provisionsnote>
  </reg:content>
</reg:regulation>